OL,3,CChippy that's keeping the price of a
OL,4,Cfish supper low for the community
OL,6,FVideo Report by Rob Smith
OL,8,FA historic chip shop in Greater
OL,9,FManchester has managed to keep prices
OL,10,Flow for customers, with just one price
OL,11,Frise of 50 pence since 2022.
OL,13,FRobbins J chippy in Leigh started life
OL,14,Fas a fish and chip shop in 1893. It
OL,15,Fhas been run by owner John Robbins,
OL,16,Ffor almost 40 years.
OL,18,FUnlike many chip shops, where prices
OL,19,Fhave soared over recent years, here
OL,20,Ffish and chips costs just six pounds.
OL,21,FA sausage is 60 pence.
