OL,3,CChippy that's keeping the price of a
OL,4,Cfish supper low for the community
OL,6,FThe shop stands at the end of a row of
OL,7,Fterraced houses on Gordon Street and
OL,8,Finside is like stepping back in time.
OL,10,FAn old fashioned price board hangs
OL,11,Fbehind the counter, along with an old
OL,12,Fhatch that was originally used to
OL,13,Fserve miners from the nearby Parsonage
OL,14,FColliery, now home to Parsonage Retail
OL,15,FPark.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
