OL,3,CChippy that's keeping the price of a
OL,4,Cfish supper low for the community
OL,6,FOther than some part-time help in the
OL,7,Fearly years, he does it all by himself.
OL,9,FJohn says customers often queue down
OL,10,Fthe street to place their orders, with
OL,11,Fhis homemade steak puddings popular
OL,12,Fwith his regulars.
OL,14,F"I know who comes in at what time and
OL,15,Fwhat they're eating. I don't know all
OL,16,Ftheir names but I know their orders!"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
