OL,3,CChippy that's keeping the price of a
OL,4,Cfish supper low for the community
OL,6,FAnother favourite with diners is the
OL,7,F'superbarm' containing fish, chips,
OL,8,Fpeas and sausage, an invention that
OL,9,Fother chippies have since copied. At
OL,10,F#2.50, his are a fraction of the
OL,11,Fprices elsewhere.
OL,13,FJohn, now 62, says doing everything
OL,14,Fhimself, including buying his fish
OL,15,Ffrom Fleetwood Market, has helped him
OL,16,Fkeep prices down. But he's not immune
OL,17,Ffrom the pressures all such businesses
OL,18,Fare facing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
