OL,3,CChippy that's keeping the price of a
OL,4,Cfish supper low for the community
OL,6,FLast week the president of the
OL,7,FNational Federation of Fish Friers
OL,8,Fwarned that traditional fish and chip
OL,9,Fshops could vanish within five years,
OL,10,Fwith many being forced to add burgers
OL,11,Fand pizzas to their menus because of
OL,12,Flower footfall and rising costs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
