OL,3,CChippy that's keeping the price of a
OL,4,Cfish supper low for the community
OL,6,FPrior to the pandemic John worked six
OL,7,Fdays a week, but since lockdown and
OL,8,Fenergy price rises he has cut down to
OL,9,Fjust two days a week: "For the last
OL,10,Fthree years I've just opened two days
OL,11,Fa week on Thursday and Friday. Rather
OL,12,Fthan six days of gas and electric, I'm
OL,13,Fjust paying two and it just means
OL,14,Fpeople come on those two days instead
OL,15,Fof being spread across the week."
OL,17,FJohn says he still enjoys the job and
OL,18,Fserving his community, who are the
OL,19,Fheart of his business: "Most people in
OL,20,Fmy street are either out of work or on
OL,21,Fminimum wage jobs," he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
