OL,3,CChippy that's keeping the price of a
OL,4,Cfish supper low for the community
OL,6,F"And you've got a lot of pensioners
OL,7,Ftoo. It's an area with first-time
OL,8,Fbuyer houses so there's not a lot of
OL,9,Fmoney around. I'm not going to ask for
OL,10,Fmore than I need to."
OL,12,F"I'll carry on as long as I can - I
OL,13,Fwould be bored if I didn't. They'll
OL,14,Fcarry me out in a box hopefully!"
OL,16,FGordon Street chippy opens on
OL,17,FThursdays and Fridays from 11.30am to
OL,18,F1.30pm and from 4.30pm to 6.30pm.
